{"tid":548422,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"何解初初都是漂亮何解初初雙眼善良","createTime":"2018-02-02T13:52:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-02T16:23:00.000Z","uid":148879,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4c5ae00370ac0bc6f960335923a98d706557f729","tid":548422,"uid":148879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T13:52:13.000Z","msg":"好多人都話女人嘅愛情係加法<br />\n男人嘅愛情係減法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前 一條親手織嘅頸巾<br />\n就會令佢心花怒放<br />\n而家 用心整嘅手工藝<br />\n喺佢心入面好似都唔算得上乜野<br />\n<br />\n原本甜蜜嘅畫面<br />\n變左一大堆嘈交嘅時候嘅氣話<br />\n小脾氣就無限放大<br />\n關心就變到一文不值<br />\n陪伴變到理所當然<br />\n<br />\n食我隻豬嗰陣係幾咁需要我<br />\n慢慢已經變到可以一邊扑野一邊同人whatsapp<br />\n可能我已經唔再新鮮唔再吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我零願你唔同我扑野<br />\n都好過咁唔尊重我<br />\n<br />\n佢講到出口話唔會再瞓身咁去愛<br />\n原來個心真係可以咁痛<br />\n最痛嘅係就算諗返起咁多<br />\n都因為太愛而無辦法放手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c5f6dee2b6c32f3bbd2e90e5129949b585c17d0","tid":548422,"uid":31921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T14:23:40.000Z","msg":"絲打識貨 還記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbetween 點樣一路扑一路wtsapp咁西利"},{"pid":"e0809612456b92656e4ce3265360a65500076661","tid":548422,"uid":148879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T14:42:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絲打識貨 還記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbetween 點樣一路扑一路wtsapp咁西利</blockquote><br />\n我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />狗仔嗰陣 仲要俾我發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0f2f2a5bcdf7fb00a89ff17e809264e154ce618","tid":548422,"uid":146726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0809612456b92656e4ce3265360a65500076661","tid":548422,"uid":148879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T14:42:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絲打識貨 還記得<img src=\"/asset